ShowBiz prices offering , to shuffle board . ShowBiz Pizza Time Inc said Friday it would sell 3 . 2 million shares of its common stock in a public offering at $ 16 . 50 per share . As announced previously , all of the shares are being sold by Hallwood Group Inc and its affiliates . ShowBiz will not receive any of the proceeds . Showbiz quoted Hallwood as saying it had elected to sell substantially all of its ShowBiz shares in this offering in order to repay debt and focus on other investments . After the closing , five members of ShowBiz ' s board affiliated with Hallwood are expected to resign , and the remaining four will elect new directors . ShowBiz said the number of directors on the board will shrink to seven from nine . 
